flowchart TB
  P["Permission Allow Executable"] --> C{"Concurrency Is concurrency safe?"}
  C -->|safe| Q["Parallel Queue concurrent queue"]
  C -->|keyed| K{"Resource Key conflicts with resources?"}
  C -->|exclusive| E["Serial Queue Serial Queue"]
  K -->|No conflict| Q
  K -->|There is conflict| E
  Q --> B{"Long Running? Long task?"}
  E --> B
  B -->|no| F["Foreground waiting at the front desk"]
  B -->|yes| G["Backgroundable background task/progress"]
  F --> X["Execute"]
  G --> X

  C:::hot
  K:::hot
